Firearm frowns as he watches Spears shake, act funny, then shake again, and 
act even wierder.

"Is it just me or does she look like she's malfunctioning?" he asks to 
Lunarpine, frowning as he watches her walk off.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
The door to the CR chamber opens and Ramulus walks out, looking around.

"How'd the attack go?" he asks, eager for news.
